Global Motors Inc saidit has agreed to become become the exclusive North Americanimporter of the Lincan Gama, a four-wheel-drive sport vehiclemanufactured by &lt;P.T. Indauda> of Indonesia.    In a letter of intent it signed with P.T. Indauda, Globalsaid it expects to begin marketing the first Lincan Gamas inmid-1989, with 20,000 units projected to be marketed in thefirst year.    Global is the parent company of Yugo America Inc, importerof the Yugoslavian Yugo vehicle. Reuter&#3;